.SH NAME
drm_atomic_helper_bridge_reset \- Allocate and initialize a bridge state to its default
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct drm_bridge_state *" drm_atomic_helper_bridge_reset
.BI "(struct drm_bridge *bridge "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bridge" 12
the bridge this state refers to
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Allocates the bridge state and initializes it to default values. This helper
is meant to be used as a bridge \fIdrm_bridge_funcs.atomic_reset\fP hook for
bridges that don't subclass the bridge state.
